{"tid":2035262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「流亡手足計劃」要獨立就要有實質行動","createTime":"2020-05-25T19:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T20:33:21.000Z","uid":258171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"08c4176a081fee3e9149ffb7d2387156c22f0fa7","tid":2035262,"uid":258171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T19:14:05.000Z","msg":"流亡手足：<br />\n我地要獨立就必須做出自己生產線<br />\n為未來十年做出第一步既行動！<br />\n黃圈發展啊唔係淨食黃店就足夠<br />\n要將生活融入黃色經濟圈<br />\n<ins></ins>衣，食，農，樂<br />\n食我地已經做到但其三方向還未開始！<br />\n我地流亡手足計劃左開始發展生產線<br />\n首先：衣<br />\n例如：<a href=\"https://instagram.com/myruleshk?igshid=u3ei9dav6jr0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fmyruleshk%3Figshid%3Du3ei9dav6jr0&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjYw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=165e895d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/myruleshk?igshid=u3ei9dav6jr0</a><br />\n買本地出品既衣服 拒絕買藍店<br />\n其次：農<br />\n例如：<a href=\"https://instagram.com/nodako.onthefarm?igshid=rlmwoed8fl7j\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fnodako.onthefarm%3Figshid%3Drlmwoed8fl7j&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjYw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=93010d45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/nodako.onthefarm?igshid=rlmwoed8fl7j</a><br />\n我地開始發展本地既農業 唔食黑心菜<br />\n最後：樂<br />\n例如：<a href=\"https://instagram.com/instinctofsight?igshid=1mssgz2pxp1m7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Finstinctofsight%3Figshid%3D1mssgz2pxp1m7&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjYw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=d500d82d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/instinctofsight?igshid=1mssgz2pxp1m7</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/ns_work_shop?igshid=vy64yq7gtwnj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fns_work_shop%3Figshid%3Dvy64yq7gtwnj&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjYw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=cbb87c81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/ns_work_shop?igshid=vy64yq7gtwnj</a><br />\n無論係玩都要幫襯自己人 <br />\n好多本地樂隊都好黃 而音樂係最容易宣揚理念<br />\n音樂容易接觸 推廣範圍廣<br />\n獨立之路一定好辛苦 你又願唔願意和我走這條路<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n香港獨立<br />\n唯一出路"},{"pid":"df7055b9b96ece868716143162985672c5c49884","tid":2035262,"uid":258171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T19:15:00.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"b10294991c7682f4252e326c3b9b6c83bcd421bc","tid":2035262,"uid":258171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T19:15:23.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"1bc3787140934335c1968bea806a4e9463f81ebd","tid":2035262,"uid":258171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T19:15:33.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"e7036312294a39c2e4ac516979b191ebbfd1fa25","tid":2035262,"uid":258171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T19:15:44.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"76a85367267cb0cc4d7b3667e93f9faa9f9c1043","tid":2035262,"uid":258171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T19:15:56.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"c12b11c06b58dfe2bed8c45c87fe4e7fd16aea36","tid":2035262,"uid":258171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T19:16:07.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"5827e6cf3e2be650f71d6b0855c265ac1b2014a0","tid":2035262,"uid":258171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T19:16:19.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"96b773e42a7d6091174930c5fe17113b77ff6fdf","tid":2035262,"uid":258171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T19:16:29.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"85cbb99096a8ffb9ad4192a0a1d09f696a88cf32","tid":2035262,"uid":258171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T19:16:42.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"2ebc472a3ccdb0d2418699a271bf55930bddacd9","tid":2035262,"uid":258171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T19:16:53.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"7d3d98baf67619d578334a6b25249377db36682d","tid":2035262,"uid":2581